{"tid":1854395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫症中的自我修養","createTime":"2020-01-31T12:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T12:52:53.000Z","uid":212365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56d7a55a9251464cc4fb1112cf805f3daebc7ab7","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天滅中共，全黨死清光！武漢肺炎必上京！</span></span><br />\nOkay入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家處於人心惶惶嘅階段 明白大家都有好多恐慌<br />\n日日數住有幾多口罩提心吊膽 諗緊自己點解仲要翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望大家可以提醒自己 即使係咁 無須搶購一切物資 提升自己嘅國民質素+社會互助精神<br />\n政府垃圾唔代表我地要自暴自棄 我地更加要團結自救<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">口罩</span></ins>之前有人已經講過唔好囤積多過<strong>三盒</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家都可以用到 有好多年長人士或者行動不便嘅人士唔係咁易排幾粒鐘+上網搵唔同渠道買<br />\n如果自己已經上網訂到夠未來2-3個月嘅用量 就唔好再出街搶喇<br />\n當然 口罩供應不足係<strong>政府嘅責任</strong><br />\n但希望大家都唔好正係顧住自己嘅生死 比多啲同理心<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">日用品及食物方面</span></ins> 同樣道理 唔好大量搶購 <br />\n你話買多少少以備不時之需非常合理 因為而家冇人知疫情會去到幾嚴重<br />\n但麻煩唔好因爲恐慌而搶<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">重點：諗下邊啲野係需要 邊啲係因為驚而買<br />\n唔好過分採購 唔好抱住一副搶咗就贏咗嘅心態</span><br />\n希望大家可以撇除香港人一貫嘅醜陋心態<br />\n見到啲人搶野/打尖/買唔到發爛渣可以出聲即刻制止<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>行動方面</strong></ins> 個人認為可以有幾個方向<br />\n1.追擊武漢P4實驗室疑似洩漏是次病毒 <br />\n2.持續文宣：勿忘運動及在過往半年各未追討的人道災難<br />\n3.追擊政府以及中共在防疫工作中的不足 嘗試令更多人&ldquo;覺醒&rdquo;及令全球再次認清呢個政權<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！康復香港！時代抗疫！</span>"},{"pid":"b0e2814b48cccb7af3794a6bcd6a5d57c847179e","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7b14b4e1991692756e1f6b8b108e5dd4be1b46","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"洗手 洗手 洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929c90a69a1107685b9c71e6cf9c75837404b7fd","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"d17e9612e925272c52fd8999eb9f8661f5247d89","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ef33cde6881888d011556baf5e382a19793984","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"唔好幫襯仆街藥房炒口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abc365668ca2dc7e676ab788c455db115bbd853","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"炒口罩者必得肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c6ab07dd7a27aad08df2d738842d403e26b710","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家都身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d02391f722d1c828dfde7351a010cdcdfd7dd","tid":1854395,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做好清潔"}]}